<div class="section" style="background:#fefbf4">
  <div class="screen-wrapper">
    <div class="faq screen">
      <div class="faq__container">
        <div class="faq__header">
          <div class="faq__label">Q&A</div>
          <h1 class="faq__title">よくあるご質問</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="faq__content">
          <div class="faq__card">
            <div class="faq__items">
              <div class="faq__item faq__item--first">
                <div class="faq__item-inner">
                  <div class="faq__item-badge"><div class="faq__item-badge-text">Q</div></div>
                  <div class="faq__item-text"><span class="faq__item-question">突然フードを切り替えても大丈夫？<br /></span><span class="faq__item-answer">今までのフードに少量混ぜ、1週間から10日<br />くらい時間をかけて切り替えてください。</span></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="faq__divider"></div>
              <div class="faq__item">
                <div class="faq__item-inner">
                  <div class="faq__item-badge"><div class="faq__item-badge-text">Q</div></div>
                  <div class="faq__item-text"><span class="faq__item-question">療法食から切り替えてもいい？<br /></span><span class="faq__item-answer">獣医師の指示なく切り替えて与えないでくだ<br />さい。</span></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="faq__divider"></div>
              <div class="faq__item">
                <div class="faq__item-inner">
                  <div class="faq__item-badge"><div class="faq__item-badge-text">Q</div></div>
                  <div class="faq__item-text"><span class="faq__item-question">どのように保管すればいい？<br /></span><span class="faq__item-answer">高温多湿を避け、直射日光が当たらない涼し<br />い場所で保管してください。</span></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="faq__divider"></div>
              <div class="faq__item">
                <div class="faq__item-inner">
                  <div class="faq__item-badge"><div class="faq__item-badge-text">Q</div></div>
                  <div class="faq__item-text"><span class="faq__item-question">原材料も国産ですか？<br /></span><span class="faq__item-answer">原材料は国産に限らず、品質基準を満たした<br />世界各国の原材料を使用しています。</span></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq__footer">
            <a href="https://www.petline.co.jp/privacy/" target="_blank"><span class="faq__footer-link">プライバシーポリシー</span></a><span class="faq__footer-spacer">&emsp;&emsp;</span><a href="https://www.petline.co.jp/regulation/" target="_blank"><span class="faq__footer-link">利用規約</span></a><span class="faq__footer-spacer">&emsp;&emsp;</span><a href="https://www.petlineonline.com/shop/pages/law.aspx" target="_blank"><span class="faq__footer-link">特定商取引法に基づく表記</span></a><br /><span class="faq__footer-copyright">&copy; 2025 ペットライン株式会社</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  /* ==========================================
     Section & Screen base styles (scoped)
     ========================================== */
  .section {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    height: 100vh;
    height: 100dvh;
    min-height: 100vh;
    min-height: 100dvh;
    padding-bottom: 55px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    scroll-snap-align: start;
  }

  .screen-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* ==========================================
     FAQ section container
     ========================================== */
  .faq {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 37px;
    width: 440px !important;
    height: 959px !important;
    overflow: hidden !important;
    background-color: var(--background-02);
    will-change: transform;
  }

  .faq__container {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 65px;
    width: 400px;
    height: 711px;
    margin-top: 101px;
    margin-left: 20px;
  }

  /* ==========================================
     Header (Q&A label + title)
     ========================================== */
  .faq__header {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 7px;
    width: fit-content;
  }

  .faq__label {
    align-self: stretch;
    color: var(--orange);
    font-size: var(--font-size-s);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.70px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .faq__title {
    align-self: stretch;
    color: var(--brown-title-text);
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1.80px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* ==========================================
     Content area & card
     ========================================== */
  .faq__content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 48px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .faq__card {
    width: 400px;
    height: 483px;
    background-color: var(--white);
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 3px 3px 5px #0000000d;
  }

  /* ==========================================
     FAQ items list
     ========================================== */
  .faq__items {
    position: relative;
    top: 34px;
    left: 21px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 23px;
    width: 358px;
  }

  .faq__item-inner {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 11px;
  }

  .faq__item-badge {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 10px;
    width: 29px;
    height: 29px;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    background-color: var(--green);
    border-radius: 14.5px;
  }

  .faq__item-badge-text {
    color: var(--white);
    font-size: var(--font-size-l);
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.80px;
  }

  .faq__item-text {
    letter-spacing: 0.45px;
    line-height: 23px;
  }

  .faq__item-question {
    color: var(--eerie-black);
    font-size: var(--font-size-m);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.07px;
  }

  .faq__item-answer {
    color: var(--eerie-black);
    font-size: var(--font-size-m);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.07px;
  }

  .faq__divider {
    align-self: stretch;
    width: 100%;
    height: 0;
    border-top: 1px dashed #d9d9d9;
  }

  /* ==========================================
     Footer links & copyright
     ========================================== */
  .faq__footer {
    color: var(--stack);
    font-size: var(--font-size-xxxs);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.10px;
    line-height: 18px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .faq__footer-link {
    letter-spacing: -0.01px;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .faq__footer-spacer {
    letter-spacing: -0.01px;
  }

  .faq__footer-copyright {
    letter-spacing: -0.01px;
  }
</style>
